    <!--== Service Page Content Start ==-->
    <section id="service-page-wrapper" class="section-padding">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <!-- Single Services Start -->
                    <div class="single-service-item">
                        <div class="service-item-thumb ser-thumb-bg-1"></div>
                        <div class="service-item-content">
                            <h3>ROAD DEDICATED</h3>
                            <p>Our vast fleet of over 6,800 road carriers forms a comprehensive safety net spread over 160 countries across Europe and beyond. Our vehicles are on the front line of emergency logistics operations across the continent – and can be with you anywhere in Europe in less than 2 hours – 24/7/365.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Single Services End -->

                    <!-- Single Services Start -->
                    <div class="single-service-item">
                        <div class="service-item-thumb ser-thumb-bg-2 d-lg-none d-md-block"></div>
                        <div class="service-item-content">
                            <h3>PREMIUM AIRFREIGHT</h3>
                            <p>This service operates worldwide, for regular-route, one-off and contingency situations. Collection and delivery on the ground are conducted securely with customs clearance also managed by us.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-item-thumb ser-thumb-bg-2 d-none d-lg-block d-md-none"></div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Single Services End -->

                    <!-- Single Services Start -->
                    <div class="single-service-item">
                        <div class="service-item-thumb ser-thumb-bg-3"></div>
                        <div class="service-item-content">
                            <h3>AIR CHARTER</h3>
                            <p>For this premium service we provide a dedicated aircraft to deliver your consignment. Your package is secure in our care from collection to delivery and is the only item on board the chartered aeroplane or helicopter. Our experts select the best aircraft for the job based on years of experience, working in conjunction with our charter partners.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Single Services End -->

                    <!-- Single Services Start -->
                    <div class="single-service-item">
                        <div class="service-item-thumb ser-thumb-bg-4 d-lg-none d-md-block"></div>
                        <div class="service-item-content">
                            <h3>HAND CARRY</h3>
                            <p>When you need the extra peace of mind that hand-delivery brings, this is the option for you. This service is ideal for small consignments, e.g. sensitive documents, data, designs or samples. Your items are entrusted to one of our operatives who personally carries them onboard a commercial flight. Available door-to-door, fully discrete and secure.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-item-thumb ser-thumb-bg-2 d-none d-lg-block d-md-none"></div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Single Services End -->
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
